name: Apex Fusion Integrates Stargate to Bring USDC Liquidity to Cardano
description: The brass saint pulls the iridescent cyan river (USDC) from the magenta Stargate nexus, achieving the holy weld. This ritual mechanics stitches the disparate chains, consecrating stable flow across the digital entropy of the AI cathedral.
